{
  "stem": "6944.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The next day, my mother visited him, and she found some [INAUDIBLE] cowered in a corner.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was frightened even to talk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was trembling.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then eventually, she told-- he told her that there was so much screaming and shouting during the night, and sc-- people being pulled out of their cells and schlepped along into the corridor and shot.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He heard shots after shots.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After a week-- yeah, the-- the people who were-- were pulled out screaming, they were communists.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Nazis wanted to erad-- eradicate communism.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was just the opposite of what they wanted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wanted the nationalism, you see.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the communists were el-- tri-- they tried to eliminate them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Also, the rumors, all rumors, that people were found shot in the gutters, str-- also pulled out from the homes, and just got-- not Jews, communists.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All communists.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Eradicate the communists because they are the enemies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, of course, it was the Juden.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "After a week, my father was transferred to a penitentiary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A penitentiary is, of course, for murderers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But-- but I don't know if they had-- didn't have any more murderers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But these sort of people, like my father and so on, who were the enemies of the country.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were taken to-- they were taken to this penitentiary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, of course, we were agitated, terribly agitated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My mother tried now to get him out, but nothing doing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had two brothers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Cologne, itself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Koln.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Koln itself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so my-- my mother contacted his two brothers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They, of course, were also very worried about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She contacted his two brothers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one brother couldn't do a thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
